":"https://avatar-cdn.atlassian.com/6a93de6d1d4b0053831945571f8ca4e6?s=48&d=https%3A%2F%2Feucalyptus.atlassian.net%2Fsecure%2Fuseravatar%3FownerId%3Dscottb%26avatarId%3D12701%26noRedirect%3Dtrue","24x24":"https://avatar-cdn.atlassian.com/6a93de6d1d4b0053831945571f8ca4e6?s=24&d=https%3A%2F%2Feucalyptus.atlassian.net%2Fsecure%2Fuseravatar%3Fsize%3Dsmall%26ownerId%3Dscottb%26avatarId%3D12701%26noRedirect%3Dtrue","16x16":"https://avatar-cdn.atlassian.com/6a93de6d1d4b0053831945571f8ca4e6?s=16&d=https%3A%2F%2Feucalyptus.atlassian.net%2Fsecure%2Fuseravatar%3Fsize%3Dxsmall%26ownerId%3Dscottb%26avatarId%3D12701%26noRedirect%3Dtrue","32x32":"https://avatar-cdn.atlassian.com/6a93de6d1d4b0053831945571f8ca4e6?s=32&d=https%3A%2F%2Feucalyptus.atlassian.net%2Fsecure%2Fuseravatar%3Fsize%3Dmedium%26ownerId%3Dscottb%26avatarId%3D12701%26noRedirect%3Dtrue"},"displayName":"Scott Butler","active":true,"timeZone":"America/Los_Angeles"},"updated":"2016-03-16T17:36:56.498-0500","status":{"self":"https://eucalyptus.atlassian.net/rest/api/2/status/1","description":"The issue is open and ready for the assignee to start work on it.","iconUrl":"https://eucalyptus.atlassian.net/images/icons/statuses/open.png","name":"Open","id":"1","statusCategory":{"self":"https://eucalyptus.atlassian.net/rest/api/2/statuscategory/2","id":2,"key":"new","colorName":"blue-gray","name":"To Do"}},"components":[],"timeoriginalestimate":null,"description":"(from Harold)\r\n\r\nImprovement - Eucalyptus Installation / Configure the Runtime Environment / Configure DNS - https://www-stage.eucalyptus-systems.com/docs/eucalyptus/4.0/index.html#shared/setting_up_dns.html\r\n\r\nA few things here:\r\n\r\n* We don't mention the following DNS properties, and if they can/can't be changed:\r\n** dns.dns_listener_address_match\r\n** dns.instancedata.enabled\r\n** dns.ns.enabled\r\n** dns.services.enabled\r\n** dns.services.hostmapping\r\n** dns.spoof_regions.enabled\r\n** dns.spoof_regions.region_name\r\n** dns.spoof_regions.spoof_aws_default_regions\r\n** dns.spoof_regions.spoof_aws_regions\r\n** dns.tcp.timeout_seconds\r\n** objectstorage.s3provider.s3usebackenddns (this is mentioned here - https://www-stage.eucalyptus-systems.com/docs/eucalyptus/4.0/index.html#shared/osg_additional_config.html - however it would be helpful if there could be a link from the 'Configure DNS' page to the 'OSG Advanced Configuration' page\r\n\r\n* Under the section 'Advanced DNS Options', we have the following:\r\n{quote}\r\nRecursive lookups and split-horizon DNS are available in Eucalyptus.\r\n\r\n1. To enable any of the DNS resolvers, set dns.enabled to true.\r\n2. To enable the recursive DNS resolver, set dns.recursive.enabled to true.\r\n3. To enable split-horizon DNS resolution for internal instance public DNS name queries, set dns.split_horizon.enabled to true.\r\n{quote}\r\nThis is the default on Eucalyptus DNS enabled/disabled clouds, so therefore this is incorrect.  I think we should update this to explain when these are actually used (i.e. are they honored when Eucalyptus DNS is disabled).\r\n\r\n* In Edge networking (https://www-stage.eucalyptus-systems.com/docs/eucalyptus/4.0/index.html#install-guide/nw_edge.html)\r\nTo change instance DNS domain, the following needs to be done:\r\n* Change the cloud property 'cloud.vmstate.instance_subdomain'\r\n{code}\r\n$ euca-modify-property -p cloud.vmstate.instance_subdomain=<instance subdomain>\r\n{code}\r\n* Update the 'InstanceDnsDomain' property in the JSON file, and upload to the cloud property 'cloud.network.network_configuration':\r\n{code}\r\n$ euca-modify-property -f cloud.network.network_configuration=</path/to/your/config_file.json>\r\n{code}\r\n\r\n","customfield_13000":null,"customfield_13200":null,"customfield_11300":null,"customfield_11500":null,"timetracking":{},"customfield_10005":null,"customfield_10401":null,"customfield_10600":null,"customfield_12900":null,"aggregatetimeestimate":null,"attachment":[],"summary":"Installation Guide: DNS Add